From 0dc5e91f865b4c2b59b69b10c082ba342dcae97e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Hariharan Ramanathan <hramanat@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 15 Jul 2025 15:08:10 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] ath12k: UPSTREAM: Fix might_sleep issue in wmm_stats read

1. Resolve checkpatch issues in ath12k_read_wmm_stats.
2. wiphy_lock has been called inside rcu_read_lock which will trigger a
   might_sleep warning.
   Move both wiphy_lock() and kzalloc() outside the rcu_read_lock to fix
   this issue.

Patch-dependency: 0130-04-UPSTREAM-DP-ath12k-sent-pkts.patch

Fixes: Ifdcf1dac12914294361ad3cee723143df11b42f4 : UPSTREAM:DP:wifi:
ath12k:Datapath stats changes for ath12k unified driver framework

Signed-off-by: Hariharan Ramanathan <hramanat@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/debugfs.c | 177 +++++++++++-----------
 1 file changed, 88 insertions(+), 89 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/debugfs.c b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/debugfs.c
